    BartNDArray, BartNDArrayView, io.github.hakkelt.ndarrays.ComplexNDArray<Float>, io.github.hakkelt.ndarrays.NDArray<org.apache.commons.math3.complex.Complex>, Iterable<org.apache.commons.math3.complex.Complex>
    public class BartNDArraySliceView
extends io.github.hakkelt.ndarrays.internal.ComplexNDArraySliceView<Float>
implements BartNDArray, BartNDArrayView
    A view for a ComplexNDArray that slices the parent ComplexNDArray. When slice(...) is called for a ComplexNDArray, an instance of this class is returned.
